# Copy to frontend/.env.local for local overrides (gitignored).
#
# Production only: the absolute backend URL. Set this in Vercel's
# Environment Variables (not committed), e.g.:
#   VITE_API_BASE=https://stock-tracker-api.onrender.com
#
# Leave it UNSET for local dev — Vite's proxy forwards /api to the
# backend on http://127.0.0.1:8001 (see vite.config.ts).
# VITE_API_BASE=
